Package repast.simphony.data2.engine

Class AggregateDataSourceWrapper

java.lang.Object
repast.simphony.data2.engine.AggregateDataSourceWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
AggregateDataSource, DataSource
public class AggregateDataSourceWrapper extends Object implements AggregateDataSource
An AggregateDataSource implementation that delegates to a wrapped AggregateDataSource for all calls except getting the id.
Author:
Nick Collier
